PublicTransport Runner
----------------------

You need KDE 4.5

-- Build instructions --

> cd runner
> mkdir build
> cd build
> cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix` ..
> make 
> make install

Restart krunner to load the runner 
> kquitapp krunner
> krunner

Alt-F2 to launch KRunner and in the runners list you will find your runner.

You might need to run kbuildsycoca4
in order to get the .desktop file recognized.
